<!--Migrate-->


After assessing your databases, the next step is to execute the migration process for the schema and database. DMA is the correct tool to use for this process.

### Process

To use DMA to create a migration project, perform the following steps.

1. Create a **New Migration** project

  a. Click on the New icon and select “Migration” project type. Select "SQL Server" as source and target types. Click "Create"

  ![New Migration](https://mpbdevcontent.azureedge.net/Images/dmamigrate.png)    
    
  b. Provide source and target SQL server conenction details. Click "Next"
  
  ![Source & Target details](https://mpbdevcontent.azureedge.net/Images/dmamigrateadddb.png)    
  
  
